.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-FEE-SKEWNESS-WEEKLY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-fee-skewness-weekly \- FEAT-2849 node-listforwards-fee-skewness-weekly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-fee-skewness-weekly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the skewness of forward fees (msat) for settled forwards in the past week for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2849).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBfee_skewness_weekly\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
